## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React, Chart.js (or D3.js)
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB (or any preferred database)
- **API**: Netflix API (or a simulated dataset)
- **Styling**: CSS3, Bootstrap/Tailwind

